<br>
&quot;Yes, Some time ago I had sought to create a masterfull gathering of wizards to form a guild to help govern the art of wizardry on norrath and give it some direction.  However things are still maturing and ripening.  In time I shall try again to establish my dream, however that time has yet to come.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;In the mean time myself and a couple other wizards have been attempting to establish a monthly meeting, a wizards council meeting if you will.  The meeting would be for wizards only and a time to socialize and trade goods and research materials, and knowledge with one anouther.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;However the few times we have attempted this it has also fallen through.  There fore I'm going to take a more direct route in trying to get tings going.  It will take time, but once the ball gets rolling.......&quot;<br>
<br>
Artillis's thoughts wander off as he smiles at the thought of multitudes of wizards gathered together.<br>
<br>
